Package: IsoDB
Type: Package
Title: Framework for Analyzing Output of PacBio Sequencing Experiments
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Kelly Cochran <kelly.cochran@duke.edu>
Maintainer: Kelly Cochran <kelly.cochran@duke.edu>
Description: Functions for assembling datasets generated from PacBio's IsoSeq
    post-sequencing pipeline, filtering out off-target and artifactual
    transcripts, and analyzing/visualizing the resulting curated
    transcriptomes. This package intends to enable researchers to easily
    convert IsoSeq output into a more interpretable format, characterize
    isoforms and isoform distributions, and compare datasets from multiple
    experiments.
